      <verse number="7" style="v" sid="OBA 1:7" />
      <char style="w" strong="H3605">Tous</char> <char style="w" strong="H0376">tes</char> <char style="w" strong="H1285">alliés</char> t’ont <char style="w" strong="H7971">chassé</char> <char style="w" strong="H5704">jusqu’</char>à la <char style="w" strong="H1366">frontière</char>, Tes <char style="w" strong="H7965">amis</char> t’<char style="w" strong="H0376">ont</char> <char style="w" strong="H5377">joué</char>, t’ont <char style="w" strong="H3201">dominé</char>, Ceux qui mangeaient ton <char style="w" strong="H3899">pain</char> t’ont <char style="w" strong="H7760">dressé</char> des <char style="w" strong="H4204">pièges</char>, Et tu n’<char style="w" strong="H8478">as</char> <char style="w" strong="H0369">pas</char> su t’en <char style="w" strong="H8394">apercevoir</char> !
